<font color="#FFFFFF">The details of every surprise attack,
every secret convoy,</font>

181
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:15,583
<font color="#FFFFFF">and every U-boat in the bloody Atlantic
go into that thing</font>

182
00:12:16,653 --> 00:12:18,921
<font color="#FFFFFF">and out comes gibberish.</font>

183
