<font color="#FFFFFF">Our Wrens intercept thousands
of radio messages a day.</font>

186
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:33,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">And to the lovely young ladies
of the Women's Royal Navy,</font>

187
00:12:33,378 --> 00:12:34,769
<font color="#FFFFFF">they're nonsense.</font>

188
00:12:35,337 --> 00:12:38,490
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's only when you feed them back
into Enigma that they make any sense.</font>

189
00:12:38,591 --> 00:12:40,243
<font color="#FFFFFF">But we have an Enigma machine.</font>

