00:12:40,342 --> 00:12:42,995
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, Polish Intelligence
smuggled it out of Berlin.</font>

191
00:12:43,096 --> 00:12:44,177
<font color="#FFFFFF">So what's the problem?</font>

192
00:12:44,221 --> 00:12:46,621
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just put the intercepted messages
back into the Enigma and...</font>

193
00:12:46,682 --> 00:12:49,668
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look, it's not that simple.
