<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll phone Denniston's office</font>

1103
01:19:40,192 --> 01:19:41,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">- so that he can alert the Admiralty.
- No.</font>

1104
01:19:41,694 --> 01:19:42,845
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you think there's enough time
