1116
01:20:07,011 --> 01:20:08,485
<font color="#FFFFFF">John, the attack is in minutes.</font>

1117
01:20:10,139 --> 01:20:11,738
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, no, I'm fine. I'm fine.</font>

1118
01:20:12,140 --> 01:20:13,658
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm fine.</font>

1119
01:20:15,019 --> 01:20:17,078
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you know why
people like violence, Hugh?</font>

1120
01:20:18,730 --> 01:20:20,957
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's because it feels good.</font>

1121
01:20:22,359 --> 01:20:26,753
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sometimes we can't do what feels good.
We have to do what is logical.</font>

1122
01:20:27,238 --> 01:20:28,506
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's logical?</font>

1123
01:20:29,073 --> 01:20:32,176
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hardest time to lie to somebody
is when they're expecting to be lied to.</font>

1124
01:20:32,744 --> 01:20:35,105
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Oh, God.
- What?</font>

1125
01:20:35,206 --> 01:20:38,274
<font color="#FFFFFF">If someone's waiting for a lie,
you can't just, er, give them one.</font>

1126
01:20:39,918 --> 01:20:41,685
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, damn it, Alan's right.</font>

1127
01:20:42,587 --> 01:20:43,988
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

1128
01:20:44,088 --> 01:20:47,909
<font color="#FFFFFF">What would the Germans think
if we destroy their U-boats?</font>

1129
01:20:48,010 --> 01:20:49,662
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nothing. They'll be dead.</font>

1130
01:20:49,761 --> 01:20:53,164
<font color="#FFFFFF">No. No, you can't be right.</font>

1131
01:20:53,265 --> 01:20:56,618
