1134
01:21:04,109 --> 01:21:06,961
<font color="#FFFFFF">What will the Germans think?</font>

1135
01:21:09,198 --> 01:21:12,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Germans will know
that we have broken Enigma.</font>

1136
01:21:12,952 --> 01:21:16,521
<font color="#FFFFFF">They'll stop all radio
communications by midday</font>

1137
01:21:16,622 --> 01:21:19,024
<font color="#FFFFFF">and they'll have changed
the design of Enigma by the weekend.</font>

1138
01:21:19,123 --> 01:21:20,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes.</font>

1139
01:21:21,918 --> 01:21:23,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">Two years' work.</font>

1140
01:21:24,212 --> 01:21:27,314
<font color="#FFFFFF">Everything that we've done here,
