1141
01:21:28,716 --> 01:21:30,902
<font color="#FFFFFF">There are 500 civilians in that convoy.</font>

1142
01:21:31,720 --> 01:21:33,529
<font color="#FFFFFF">Women, children.</font>

1143
01:21:35,140 --> 01:21:36,542
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're about to let them die.</font>

1144
01:21:36,641 --> 01:21:40,212
<font color="#FFFFFF">Our job is not to save
one passenger convoy,</font>

1145
01:21:40,311 --> 01:21:42,213
<font color="#FFFFFF">it is to win the war.</font>

1146
01:21:42,314 --> 01:21:45,541
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Our job was to crack Enigma.
- Well, we've done that.</font>

1147
01:21:47,319 --> 01:21:49,087
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now for the hard part.</font>

1148
01:21:50,780 --> 01:21:52,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Keeping it a secret.
