1149
01:21:53,826 --> 01:21:55,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

1150
01:21:55,578 --> 01:21:58,189
<font color="#FFFFFF">The convoy you're about to...
It's, er...</font>

1151
01:21:58,288 --> 01:22:00,722
<font color="#FFFFFF">The HMS Carlisle is
